1. *Govoreći* istinu, on je uvrijedio svog prijatelja. (Speaking the truth, he offended his friend.)
2. Ona je *govoreći* tiho, pjevušila pjesmu. (She was singing a song *speaking* softly.)
3. *Govoreći* iskreno, ja ne vjerujem u to. ( *Speaking* honestly, I don't believe in that.)
4. *Govoreći* o budućnosti, planiramo putovanje sljedeće godine. ( *Talking* about the future, we're planning a trip next year.)
5. Iako je bio umoran, *govoreći* tiho, uspio je završiti posao. (Although he was tired, *speaking* softly, he managed to finish the job.)
6. *Govoreći* o hrani, ova torta je najukusnija koju sam ikada probao. ( *Talking* about food, this cake is the most delicious I've ever tasted.)
7. Njegov glas je bio nejasan, *govoreći* kroz zube. (His voice was muffled, *speaking* through his teeth.)
8. *Govoreći* istovremeno, nitko nije mogao čuti što su govorili. ( *Speaking* at the same time, no one could hear what they were saying.)
9. On je bio oprezan, *govoreći* polako i promišljeno. (He was cautious, *speaking* slowly and thoughtfully.)
10. *Govoreći* iskreno, ona mu je rekla što osjeća. ( *Speaking* honestly, she told him how she felt.)